INTRODUCTION
Play Swing Copters on your Google Chrome Browser with our simple & lightweight extension - No Internet required, no ADS, and 100% Free!

HOW TO INSTALL?
1. Click "Add to Chrome" to install the extension
2. Pin the Swing Copters extension icon to the Chrome toolbar
3. Click the Swing Copters icon on the Chrome toolbar, the Swing Copters popup will open. 
That's all you need to do! Have fun!

You also can play more games from the top-left menu
